@XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5212

### Start workflow (streamId + workflowId)
POST {{XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/start/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/42
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowName": "Sample Workflow"
}

###

### Complete workflow step
POST {{XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/42/step-completed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stepNumber": 2
}

###

### Complete workflow
POST {{XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/42/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "finalStatus": "Completed"
}

###

### Get workflow details by stream ID + workflow ID
GET {{XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/42

###

### Get workflow event history
GET {{XFlow.Insights.API_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/42/events
###
